{"tid":802711,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關公屋戶主離世而轉戶主既問題","createTime":"2018-09-01T15:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T11:31:34.000Z","uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a84b29041674d9c24bdd57031425b9ba64671689","tid":802711,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"自細家庭離異，之後老豆一個人排左間公屋自己住<br />\n近幾年老豆身體越黎越差，都成70，所以就透過共享天倫計劃，加左個名去個公屋戶藉度搬過去住當照顧老豆<br />\n如果戶主，姐係老豆不幸過左身，假設通過入息審查(收入57700+資產1160000以下)，係咪可以申請自己做戶主? <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">其實我係幫朋友問，但唔想下下用第三人稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"8673766674de23da94190d6be85126375f86140c","tid":802711,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9364c4fddba5583641334f0fe724fa09d7750ff4","tid":802711,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4b23b61d9fbd48947ece0b8c1d2ee081f9c3ff","tid":802711,"uid":191900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"依家戶藉入面得爸爸同朋友？"},{"pid":"0707b8901a1e96d22f57229046122cd833a9df5b","tid":802711,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4b23b61d9fbd48947ece0b8c1d2ee081f9c3ff","tid":802711,"uid":191900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"依家戶藉入面得爸爸同朋友？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"根據佢所講，係"},{"pid":"089fe0c337ef2c6985060a55681e5cad3ec4d311","tid":802711,"uid":191900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0707b8901a1e96d22f57229046122cd833a9df5b","tid":802711,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4b23b61d9fbd48947ece0b8c1d2ee081f9c3ff","tid":802711,"uid":19190